| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5543 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 80c6f992-dbcc-5f60-a36c-09ed7a9239b8"
